  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/91d5d2e6c7dc5304df8279f26be0875c.avif?t=1742431241\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras_big/91d5d2e6c7dc5304df8279f26be0875c.avif?t=1742431241 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to immerse yourself in the high-stakes world of horse racing! <strong>Tap Derby</strong> puts you in control as you <strong>buy, train, and race your way to Horse Racing Stardom</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏇</strong> <strong>Begin Your Legacy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1076568359afa4ac6e868a0e43cc510b.poster.avif?t=1742431241\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1076568359afa4ac6e868a0e43cc510b.webm?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1076568359afa4ac6e868a0e43cc510b.mp4?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your journey at the auction house, where you'll purchase your first horse with the expert guidance of legendary trainer Rusty Hayes. Every decision matters—can you spot the next champion?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏆 <strong>Train, Race, Dominate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/5d1f53aac668c3ca48ef7d445545a0b0.poster.avif?t=1742431241\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/5d1f53aac668c3ca48ef7d445545a0b0.webm?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/5d1f53aac668c3ca48ef7d445545a0b0.mp4?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your stable and train your horses to perfection, mastering the balance of speed, stamina, and agility. Outsmart and outrun your rivals as you compete in thrilling races, from the maiden ranks to prestigious championships.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💗<strong> Build Champion Pedigrees</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1a4462474cb3b20f5cc348cd89f98c94.poster.avif?t=1742431241\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1a4462474cb3b20f5cc348cd89f98c94.webm?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1a4462474cb3b20f5cc348cd89f98c94.mp4?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sustain on-track success with brilliant breeding. Pair your top performers together or breed to outside studs to develop elite bloodlines excelling in speed, stamina, and agility. Carefully select sires and dams to refine traits across generations. Will you build a legacy of unstoppable sprinters, enduring distance runners, or well-rounded champions? The choices you make will shape the future of your racing empire!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎖️ <strong>Chase Glory</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/40ffea141375b110b93a22a56e0f448d.poster.avif?t=1742431241\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/40ffea141375b110b93a22a56e0f448d.webm?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/40ffea141375b110b93a22a56e0f448d.mp4?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the adrenaline of winning iconic events, like the Tap Derby, Tapper's Cup, and international festivals. Watch your trophy case grow as you rise through the ranks and establish your legacy as a racing legend.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/91d5d2e6c7dc5304df8279f26be0875c.avif?t=1742431241\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras_big/91d5d2e6c7dc5304df8279f26be0875c.avif?t=1742431241 width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to immerse yourself in the high-stakes world of horse racing! <strong>Tap Derby</strong> puts you in control as you <strong>buy, train, and race your way to Horse Racing Stardom</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏇</strong> <strong>Begin Your Legacy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1076568359afa4ac6e868a0e43cc510b.poster.avif?t=1742431241\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1076568359afa4ac6e868a0e43cc510b.webm?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/1076568359afa4ac6e868a0e43cc510b.mp4?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your journey at the auction house, where you'll purchase your first horse with the expert guidance of legendary trainer Rusty Hayes. Every decision matters—can you spot the next champion?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏆 <strong>Train, Race, Dominate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/5d1f53aac668c3ca48ef7d445545a0b0.poster.avif?t=1742431241\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstati