extras/40ffea141375b110b93a22a56e0f448d.poster.avif?t=1742431241\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/40ffea141375b110b93a22a56e0f448d.webm?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362320/extras/40ffea141375b110b93a22a56e0f448d.mp4?t=1742431241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the adrenaline of winning iconic events, like the Tap Derby, Tapper's Cup, and international festivals. Watch your trophy case grow as you rise through the ranks and establish your legacy as a racing legend.</p>",
